        account.company

        Parameters:
        address -

        The company’s primary address.

        account.company.address

        addressKana -

        The Kana variation of the company’s primary address (Japan only).

        https://stripe.com/docs/api/tokens/create_account#create_account_token-account-company-address_kana

        addressKanji -

        The Kanji variation of the company’s primary address (Japan only).

        https://stripe.com/docs/api/tokens/create_account#create_account_token-account-company-address_kanji

        directorsProvided -

        Whether the company’s directors have been provided. Set this Boolean to true after creating all the company’s directors with the Persons API for accounts with a relationship.director requirement. This value is not automatically set to true after creating directors, so it needs to be updated to indicate all directors have been provided.

        https://stripe.com/docs/api/tokens/create_account#create_account_token-account-company-directors_provided

        executivesProvided -

        Whether the company’s executives have been provided. Set this Boolean to true after creating all the company’s executives with the Persons API for accounts with a relationship.executive requirement.

        https://stripe.com/docs/api/tokens/create_account#create_account_token-account-company-executives_provided

        name -

        The company’s legal name.

        account.company.name

        nameKana -

        The Kana variation of the company’s legal name (Japan only).

        https://stripe.com/docs/api/tokens/create_account#create_account_token-account-company-name_kana

        nameKanji -

        The Kanji variation of the company’s legal name (Japan only).

        https://stripe.com/docs/api/tokens/create_account#create_account_token-account-company-name_kanji

        ownersProvided -

        Whether the company’s owners have been provided. Set this Boolean to true after creating all the company’s owners with the Persons API for accounts with a relationship.owner requirement.

        https://stripe.com/docs/api/tokens/create_account#create_account_token-account-company-owners_provided

        phone -

        The company’s phone number (used for verification).

        account.company.phone

        taxId -

        The business ID number of the company, as appropriate for the company’s country. (Examples are an Employer ID Number in the U.S., a Business Number in Canada, or a Company Number in the UK.)

        https://stripe.com/docs/api/tokens/create_account#create_account_token-account-company-tax_id

        taxIdRegistrar -

        The jurisdiction in which the tax_id is registered (Germany-based companies only).

        https://stripe.com/docs/api/tokens/create_account#create_account_token-account-company-tax_id_registrar

        vatId -

        The VAT number of the company.

        https://stripe.com/docs/api/tokens/create_account#create_account_token-account-company-vat_id

        verification -

        Information on the verification state of the company.

        account.company.verification

      • getDirectorsProvided

        public java.lang.Boolean getDirectorsProvided()

        Whether the company’s directors have been provided. Set this Boolean to true after creating all the company’s directors with the Persons API for accounts with a relationship.director requirement. This value is not automatically set to true after creating directors, so it needs to be updated to indicate all directors have been provided.

        https://stripe.com/docs/api/tokens/create_account#create_account_token-account-company-directors_provided
